{"tid":2192180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府毒理化驗師：陳彥霖遺體未驗出常見精神藥物和毒物 迷暈氣體因會流失難判死前狀況","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T11:52:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed67e308581e8fe280c0eb2f76c27c3f98acad9","tid":2192180,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"政府毒理化驗師指陳彥霖遺體未驗出常見藥物和毒物<br />\n最後更新時間 07.09.2020 10:56<br />\n<br />\n知專設計學院學生陳彥霖的死因庭聆訊續審，再傳召政府化驗所毒理化驗師康祐軒作供，他指為陳彥霖遺體檢取的胸腔液、膀胱沖洗液和肝臟樣本中，都未有發現常見藥物和毒物，包括氯胺酮、海洛英、可卡因和大麻，或常見抗精神病和抗抑鬱藥物，亦未有發現可迷暈的氣體包括哥羅芳等。康祐軒指，<span class=\"gold\">可以確定陳彥霖死前5天沒有吸食大麻。</span><br />\n<br />\n死因庭裁判官問及，若果死者死前吸入致命份量的有毒氣體如哥羅芳，是否可在檢驗中驗出，康祐軒指如果屍體腐化情況嚴重，<span class=\"gold\">有可能在腐化過程中流失有關氣體而無法檢驗，藥物檢測結果呈陰性不代表沒有服用過。</span>陳彥霖母親今日並未出庭，裁判官視作她沒有結案陳詞，將於星期五起總結證供並向陪審團提供指引。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2356062&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b6933320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356062</a>"},{"pid":"a9cfc94fc6b0170383d4655571910246ab5e45cb","tid":2192180,"uid":1988,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"連膀胱都有液體sample <br />\n唯獨係肺冇<br />\n食屎喇港共狗賊"},{"pid":"78fa47ca497931e7fb310d0f65634839888be191","tid":2192180,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">919 彥霖曾邀請朋友當晚去元朗住所BBQ<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2188963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2188963</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聲稱接載彥霖的 的士司機 &mdash; 供詞有疑點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2187428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2187428</a>"},{"pid":"c3d871a4b90e289a4cd4525f06fff6b71c4b95b1","tid":2192180,"uid":301152,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"専家證人馬宣立法醫：<br />\n冇做矽藻測試, <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">女屍赤裸是很大疑點</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185080</a>"},{"pid":"fa743388d7ada3e335af325332ae2198b895bf02","tid":2192180,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"納粹法醫故意唔驗咩項目就等於用咩方式殺人<br />\n<br />\n陰道有傷無精液就應該係用警棍等隊到下體出血<br />\n可能因感染而死亡"},{"pid":"97c0e71bbd1c73057cf4cac7b8afb7f0b998b7f9","tid":2192180,"uid":301152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">書生分析</span> (有關精神科何醫生報告)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2752899788312331/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2054342341501416%2Fposts%2F2752899788312331%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e8a5a3e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2752899788312331/?d=n</a><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"large\">詳見連結內文</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHRAmpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHRAmpO.jpg&h=f1665baa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f175099bad05ad5dae5ea170ef455b2da0fe2b1","tid":2192180,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"衞生署法醫李毓樺則供稱，屍體於去年9月22日撈獲當日送往域多利公眾殮房，他當時是<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\">實習法醫</span></span>，他同月24日在上司資深法醫賴世澤的監督下，在域多利驗屍，其後共同撰寫解剖報告。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局代表大狀馮國礎質疑，李在資深法醫陪同下進行解剖，其間警方鑑證科人員共拍攝了28張相，<span class=\"violet\">為何卻沒有拍攝屍體的肺及胃<br />\n</span>。<br />\n<br />\n李回應指，因屍肺沒有腫脹，且腐爛程度達輕度至中度，<span class=\"violet\">他認為沒有特別，故沒要求拍攝。 <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"06748e5c83ebe756801d33c8f112c360d4e0a8af","tid":2192180,"uid":146257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:09:28.000Z","msg"